channel.title: New project from stickywicky - project-rebirth , brining origional 317's back!
channel.description:
hi, of those that saw my other project relased i will be releasing v2 :P any way on to the new project ============================================================================== my goal: after hearing people talk about how 317 have been "ruined" by customs ect.. my goal is to bring the old 317 back (as in the title) so have the old layouts the original screen that has your messages your members credits left.... my overall dream tohugh is to make this server a more used 317 more used the the curent PI's and Delta's ... sounds impossible but with the right work i think it can be possible
the new project is a project insanity
what is the project about? well since alot of poeple actually want a origional 317 without customs like godswords and capes ect... thats what im going to do !
what will my ner project conatain ? well every monster (npc) will be will be placed like old rs 317 so cows in cow field chickens in chicken coops and evan unicorns next to barbairan village
this sounds boring! why do it? well those that have played a world of warcraft server most just have higher exp rates and some shops well my server will be similar but shops will be placed in the correct place for example zaff the staff trader will sell all staffs but he will be inside the hut
team -------- "coders" stickywicky (your name here :P )
so if you want to know more about the project or whish to help out contact me via msn or pm or reply
positions im looking for
shop coder (i cannot do shops) client designer (i cannot code clients)
note* the client designer will be deleting all custom models changing background to the old 317 login then the login popup box after loging in and edeting the game frame :)
i would do this myself but i do have a server to run so i am trying to equal out my time :)
